info.name: SE Mog Station & Store Dark Style (FFXIV)
info.description:
Dark style for Square Enix Mog Station and Online Store, which lacks this feature. Used original SE palette from Lodestone.

If you want to report bug or suggest some QoL feature: Discord  Sylfae#8557

Replaced most bright yellow colors with more dark-ish blue colors.

White buttons in Online Store is a static images and won't be changed (unless someone want to make new)
